  <travelInformation><![CDATA[<p>All our holidays include return travel to resort either by flight or train and then the transfer between the airport or railway station and Tignes.</p>
<p>All departures are on Saturdays with stays for 7 or 14 nights except our 8 night Eurostar Snow Train package which departs Saturday and returns a week late on the Sunday.</p>
<p>Private transfers and self drive options are available, call to book these.</p>
<p>Please note: The ski bus doesn’t cover all areas, the evening bus runs all night, there is parking but not free and there’s no local car hire available.</p>]]></travelInformation>
